parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, and even fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly without warning
often when the brake pedal is depressed
and may continue to accelerate even when the brake pedal is pressed harder. The engine RPM may increase rapidly
and the vehicle may lurch forward or crash into other objects.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents, injuries, and even fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal may feel soft or spongy
the brake pedal may stick to the floor
or the vehicle may not stop when the brake pedal is pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic throttle control system can cause unintended acceleration, accidents, injuries, and even fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may accelerate suddenly without warning
often when the brake pedal is depressed
and may continue to accelerate even when the brake pedal is pressed harder. The engine RPM may increase rapidly
and the vehicle may lurch forward or crash into other objects.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause accidents, injuries, and even fatalities.
symptoms: The cruise control system may disengage suddenly
causing the vehicle to decelerate rapidly
or may fail to disengage
causing the vehicle to continue accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water spot buildup on windows can obstruct driver visibility, leading to accidents or unsafe vehicle operation.
symptoms: Water spots on windows
including the windshield
side windows
and rear window.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning sun visor can obstruct driver visibility, leading to accidents or unsafe vehicle operation.
symptoms: Sun visor does not stay in the up position
falls down while driving
or hangs at eye level.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning windshield wipers can reduce driver visibility, leading to accidents or unsafe vehicle operation.
symptoms: Wipers make an abnormal noise
seize to operate
or fail to clear water from the windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning defroster and heating system can reduce driver visibility, leading to accidents or unsafe vehicle operation.
symptoms: Defroster and heating system do not work in cold temperatures
causing windshield and windows to fog up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning windshield wiper transmission can reduce driver visibility, leading to accidents or unsafe vehicle operation.
symptoms: Windshield wiper transmission is defective and needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system and unintended acceleration can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle accelerates unexpectedly
the engine revs loudly
and the vehicle fails to stop or slows down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate brake performance can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially in emergency braking situations.
symptoms: The brake pedal has to be pressed very hard
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle takes longer to stop
and the brake performance is inconsistent.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design of the brake and accelerator pedals can lead to pedal misapplication, which can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal is too close to the accelerator pedal
the foot can easily slip from the brake pedal to the accelerator pedal
and the vehicle accelerates unexpectedly.
